<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>超越博客排行</title>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="bootstrap-3.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./icon-font/iconfont.css">
	<script type="text/javascript" src="jquery.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="bootstrap-3.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<style type="text/css">
		.logo{
			vertical-align: middle;
		}
		.logo span{
			font-size: 35px;
			color: blue;
		}
		.logo a{
			text-decoration: none;
			font-size: 23px;
			color: white;
		}
		.top{
			position: fixed;
			top: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 50px;
			background-color: #000;
			z-index: 999;
		}
		.txt{
			height: 100%;
			color: white;
		}
		.txt li{
			vertical-align: middle;
		}
		.txt li:last-child input{
			color: #000;
		}
		.txt button{
			background-color: #000;
			border: none;
		}
		.txt span{
			line-height: 50px;
		}
		.txt span a{
			color: white;
		}
		.navbar{
			margin-top: 50px;
		}
		.bgtop{
			margin-top: -20px;
		}
		table{
			width: 100%;
		}
		table tr{
			height: 160px;
		}
		.but1,.but2{
			height: 80px;
			border: none;
			cursor: pointer;
		}
		.but2{
			border-bottom: 3px solid blue;
			color: blue;
		}

		.iconfont{
			font-size: 16px;
		}
		table tr td:first-child{
			position: relative;
		}
		table tr:first-child td:first-child::after{
			content: "NO.1";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			display: block;
			width: 130px;
			height: 50px;
			text-align: center;
			color: white;
			line-height: 50px;
			border-radius: 0 30px 30px 0;
			background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #d3b36a , #edd190);
		}
		table tr:nth-child(2) td:first-child::after{
			content: "NO.2";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			display: block;
			width: 130px;
			height: 50px;
			color: white;	
			text-align: center;
			line-height: 50px;
			border-radius: 0 30px 30px 0;
			background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #c9c9c9 , #dbdad8);
		}
		table tr:nth-child(3) td:first-child::after{
			content: "NO.3";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			display: block;
			width: 130px;
			height: 50px;
			color: white;
			text-align: center;
			line-height: 50px;
			border-radius: 0 30px 30px 0;
			background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #d39e6a , #efbf8e);
		}
		table tr td:first-child::after{
			content: "4";
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			display: block;
			width: 130px;
			height: 160px;
			line-height: 160px;
			color: gray;
			text-align: center;
			border-radius: 0 30px 30px 0;
		}
		.final{
			background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.5);
			margin-top: 30px;
			width: 100%;
			height: 80px;
		}
		.footul{
			margin: 0;
		}
		.context{
			height: 80px;
			color: #000;
		}
		.context ul{
			height: 80px;
			line-height: 80px;
		}
		.context a{
			color: #000;
		}
		.name{
			display: inline-block;
			text-indent: 2em;
		}

		/*模态框*/
		.time{
			display: inline-block;
			height: 26px;
			width: 28%;
			line-height: 26px;
			border: 1px solid #000;
			float: right;
		}
		.title{
			width: 65%;
		}
		.modal-content{
			padding-left: 25px;
			padding-right: 25px;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}
		.art{
			width: 100%;
			height: 450px;
		}
		/*-----------------*/
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('header') %>
<div class="container">
	<div class="col-md-6 text-center but1">
		<h3>博文排行</h3>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-6 text-center but2">
		<h3>博客排行</h3>
	</div>
</div>
		

<div class="container">
	<table class="table-responsive table-bordered">
		<tr>
			<td class="col-md-5 text-center">
				<img src="images/header.jpg" class="img-circle" style="width: 80px;height: 80px;">
				<span class="name">Amumu</span>
			</td>
			<td class="col-md-3 text-center">
				<span class="iconfont">&#xe62f;&nbsp;</span><span>25</span>
			</td>
			<td class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<span class="iconfont">&#xe640;&nbsp;</span><span>229834</span>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</div>



<div class="final footer">
	<div class="container text-center context">
		<ul class="list-inline footul">
			<li>
				<span>
					链接：<a href="">首页</a>|<a href="">排行</a>|<a href="">我的博客</a>|<a href="">我的游戏</a>		
				</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span>版权所有&nbsp;海南椰子蓬勃发展有限公司Copyright Reserved 2015-2017 苏ICP备14085412</span>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>